      <title>策略在宣布首选产品后购买更多比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/strategy-buys-more-bitcoin-after-announcing-preferred-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·塞勒（Michael Saylor）的策略表示，它在揭幕计划发行多达210亿美元的优先股以获取更多加密货币的计划后一周购买了1,070万美元的比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/strategy-buys-more-bitcoin-after-announcing-preferred-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 12:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bumble在约会应用程序安全推动中推出ID验证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/bumble-rolls-out-id-verification-in-dating-app-safety-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bumble Inc.正在将ID验证与其他新功能一起添加到其约会应用程序中，该功能试图为安全意识符合安全的年轻用户提供，这是该公司周转计划的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/bumble-rolls-out-id-verification-in-dating-app-safety-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克拉纳·德斯罗尼斯（Klarna dethrones）确认现在就可以购买，稍后在沃尔玛付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/klarna-dethrones-affirm-to-offer-buy-now-pay-later-at-walmart</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Klarna Group PLC与沃尔玛公司（Walmart Inc.）支持的Onepay合作，向美国购物者提供购买 - 付费者，以取代确认为零售巨头的快速信用选项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/klarna-dethrones-affirm-to-offer-buy-now-pay-later-at-walmart</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 11:58:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电报首席执行官杜罗夫（Durov）返回法国犯罪调查中的迪拜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/telegram-ceo-durov-returns-to-dubai-amid-french-criminal-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电报的亿万富翁创始人兼首席执行官帕维尔·杜罗夫（Pavel Durov）在阿拉伯联合酋长国，他是公民，因为法国暂时放松了与他的消息传递应用程序有关的犯罪调查的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/telegram-ceo-durov-returns-to-dubai-amid-french-criminal-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 11:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其计划新的大型技术法规，冒着与我们发生冲突的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/turkey-plans-new-big-tech-regulations-that-risk-clash-with-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其正在计划新规定，以遏制主要科技公司的统治地位，模仿欧盟的监管方法，冒着激发美国报复的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/turkey-plans-new-big-tech-regulations-that-risk-clash-with-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 11:16:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
